	(498,64,'section_one_title','TERRORISM IS A GROWING CONCERN'),
	(499,64,'_section_one_title','field_5be6ec1d676fb'),
	(500,64,'section_one_body','The Indisputable fact is that that globally the world is becoming more dangerous and every day a terrorist attack is carried out somewhere in the world.\r\n\r\nCoupled with the risk of violent criminal attacks in every major city in the world, Security and Intelligence Services with its vast intelligence resources and Close Protection personnel, are there to secure your safety. We provide highly trained and vastly experienced Close Protection officers, all of whom are from military or UK specialist agency backgrounds, on short or long term deployments worldwide.\r\n\r\nWorking with the SIS Travel Intelligence Division and our international intelligence partners, SIS provides an up to date synopsis of the security situation to wherever in world our clients may be travelling.'),
