	(597,67,'_section_two_title','field_5be6f036c9d5c'),
	(598,67,'section_two_body','The SIS team in China is headed by Allen Xie, one of a group of young, dynamic, professionals who have revolutionised the Chinese security and electronics industry in recent years.\r\n\r\nThey are the ambassadors for SIS in China and will ensure your business is carried out with complete confidence and which can save you a great deal of time and finance.\r\n\r\nIf you are considering visiting or procurement from China we can assist you in many you in many ways including:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Sourcing Products and Manufacturers.</li>\r\n 	<li>Assisting with Product Design and Samples</li>\r\n 	<li>Independent inspections of companies</li>\r\n 	<li>Arranging Hotels and Travel - IATA</li>\r\n 	<li>Interpreters</li>\r\n 	<li>Legal Issues</li>\r\n 	<li>Private Chauffeur Driven Vehicles</li>\r\n 	<li>Airport or Hong Kong Pick Up</li>\r\n 	<li>Invitations and Visas</li>\r\n 	<li>Health Advice</li>\r\n</ul>'),
