	(673,118,'_section_two','field_5be6f203e0823'),
	(674,118,'section_three_title','MAJOR TEAM ENQUIRY INVESTIGATIONS AND CORPORATE INVESTIGATIONS'),
	(675,118,'_section_three_title','field_5be6f261e0829'),
	(676,118,'section_three_body','Government Departments, Public Enquiries, Local Authorities, Hospital Authorities, Blue Chip companies and other commercial organisations can benefit by using SIS for major enquiries which is a highly professional and confidential service. We will provide regular confidential briefings and reports to clients’ senior executives if required and at the end of the enquiry we will submit a comprehensive report of our findings for internal use or for publishing if required.\r\n\r\nSIS Major Investigations are carried out by highly experienced detectives, all of whom are former specialist police and law enforcement officers from the United Kingdom, the European Union and the USA.\r\n\r\nEach one of our team of Detective Officers are former career officers who have managed or played a significant part in major criminal investigations including terrorist offences, murder, and other serious crime including complex fraud enquiries where discretion and perseverance are essential qualities\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Senior Investigating Officers</li>\r\n 	<li>Trained Investigators &amp;Financial Investigators</li>\r\n 	<li>Intelligence Analysts</li>\r\n 	<li>Statement Readers</li>\r\n 	<li>Experienced Interviewers</li>\r\n 	<li>Exhibit Officers</li>\r\n 	<li>Scenes of Crime and Forensic Officers</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nCoupled with the SIS Data Intelligence and Security Screening service we specialise in skilled, professional and confidential investigations to the commercial, corporate and government agency sectors worldwide.'),
	(677,118,'_section_three_body','field_5be6f26ce082a'),
	(678,118,'section_three_image','140'),
	(679,118,'_section_three_image','field_5be6f27ce082b'),
	(680,118,'section_three',''),
	(681,118,'_section_three','field_5be6f252e0828'),
	(682,118,'section_four_title','CORPORATE AND COMMERCIAL INVESTIGATIONS'),
	(683,118,'_section_four_title','field_5be6f299fa8aa'),
	(684,118,'section_four_body','Investigations in the corporate and commercial world are by their very nature usually highly confidential matters which could cost companies or individuals millions of pounds in lost revenue or incalculable damage to corporate or individual reputations. These types of investigations require absolute confidentiality, discretion, tact, diplomacy and innovation. SIS has unique experience in these matters\r\n\r\nAfter an initial confidential discussion with our clients, usually by our Managing Director, or one of our senior directors, an agreed plan of action is drawn up to move forward. SIS investigations are carried out by highly experienced career detectives, all of whom are former specialist police and law enforcement officers from the United Kingdom, the European Union and the USA.\r\n\r\nEach one of our team of Detective Officers are former career officers who have managed or played a significant part in major criminal investigations including terrorist offences, murder, other serious crime and complex frauds.\r\n\r\nIn addition to the specialist officers (outlined above in Major Team Investigations) SIS also have the ability to deploy highly trained and experienced undercover male and female officers on short or long-term deployments if the circumstances warrant this service. SIS also maintain a technical services capability using the very latest technology in investigative operations.\r\n\r\nCoupled with the SIS Data Intelligence and Security Screening service we specialise in skilled, professional and confidential investigations to the commercial, corporate and government agency sectors worldwide.'),
