	(728,142,'section_two_body','SIS specialise in a full range of armoured VIP 4 x 4 SUV’s Saloon Cars, and Luxury Armoured People Carriers, up to and including the internationally recognised and EU accredited standard of BR7.\r\n\r\nSIS also design and supply a full range of 4 x 4 SUV Vehicles, Pick Up Trucks and other vehicles for specialist tasks for our client’s requirements.\r\n\r\nAll of these vehicles are individually tailored to the clients’ requirements, and SIS are specialists in Satellite Communications, Internal Oxygen Systems, Specialist Night Vision Equipment, Anti-Attack External Explosive Devices and Emergency Medical Systems. We provide full training on all these systems in country.'),
