	(752,142,'section_three_title','ARMOURED VEHICLE TRAINING AND MAINTENANCE'),
	(753,142,'_section_three_title','field_5be6f5fc27957'),
	(754,142,'section_three_body','SIS specialise in delivering training packages in any operational theatre in the world including the driving and maintenance of armoured vehicles which is an integral part of our armoured vehicle package.\r\n\r\nDriving armoured vehicles safely, particularly when VIP passengers are on board is a particular skill which SIS teams regularly deliver in country.\r\n\r\nThese courses, together with our close protection instructors are designed to equip all drivers and escorts engaged in these type of operations, with the necessary skills and confidence to deal with all situations.'),
	(755,142,'_section_three_body','field_5be6f60427958'),
	(756,142,'section_three_note','All of our instructors deployed to deliver these training courses are highly experienced former Special Forces military personnel.'),
