	(858,193,'header',''),
	(859,193,'_header','field_5be70089b0994'),
	(860,193,'section_one_title','LEADERS IN OVERT AND COVERT'),
	(861,193,'_section_one_title','field_5be700af9070e'),
	(862,193,'section_one_body','SIS are at the forefront of design and technology in covert and overt surveillance systems of all types.\r\n\r\nCovert surveillance systems for all types of vehicles including vans, 4 x4 SUV’s, saloon cars, motorcycles and marine craft are designed to our clients’ requirements and specifications for operational use in any terrain, and weather conditions.\r\n\r\nThese systems can include a wide range of day/night/infrared video cameras, integrated transmission, and recording systems, intercept capabilities and GPS monitoring systems.\r\n\r\nStreet scene covert surveillance systems, covert body worn systems and rapidly deployed systems complement the vehicle systems when operating in surveillance teams or in undercover roles.'),
	(863,193,'_section_one_body','field_5be700bb9070f'),
	(864,193,'section_one_features_0_title','Full Operational Systems'),
	(865,193,'_section_one_features_0_title','field_5be700d190711'),
	(866,193,'section_one_features_0_body','We work closely with the manufacturers and designers of control rooms and back office equipment to bring our clients the complete systems for operational use on the ground and remote monitoring.'),
	(867,193,'_section_one_features_0_body','field_5be700db90712'),
	(868,193,'section_one_features_1_title','Training'),
	(869,193,'_section_one_features_1_title','field_5be700d190711'),
	(870,193,'section_one_features_1_body','We provide all training packages which are delivered by our own technicians and experienced surveillance officers from former law enforcement backgrounds.'),
	(871,193,'_section_one_features_1_body','field_5be700db90712'),
	(872,193,'section_one_features_2_title','Vehicle Integration'),
	(873,193,'_section_one_features_2_title','field_5be700d190711'),
	(874,193,'section_one_features_2_body','Overt surveillance vehicles for use in monitoring crowd control, or other similar overt functions are also designed and designed to our clients’ requirements which can include mast mounted video camera systems, high intensity floodlighting, and for the added protection of the crews this type of overt vehicle can be armoured, and fitted with anti–attack systems.'),
	(875,193,'_section_one_features_2_body','field_5be700db90712'),
