	(1040,243,'section_one_title','A WORLD CLASS TRAINING SERVICE'),
	(1041,243,'_section_one_title','field_5be8668d97967'),
	(1042,243,'section_one_body','Our highly experienced training teams drawn from Military Special Forces and Law Enforcement design and deliver bespoke courses from our training facilities in the United Kingdom, Europe and Israel.\r\n\r\nAll of our training courses are comprehensive, demanding and prepares our clients and their protection teams the highest level of professional training.\r\n\r\nWe have conducted this type of training throughout the world and at the request of our clients we will deploy teams of instructors to clients’ home states to design deliver training anywhere in the world.'),
