	(1048,243,'section_two_title','AVAILABLE TRAINING COURSES'),
	(1049,243,'_section_two_title','field_5be866bf9796b'),
	(1050,243,'section_two_body','There is no substitution for the highest level of training and preparedness before travelling and SIS will train our clients, their staff and families during a bespoke Hostile Environment Awareness Training course (HEAT).'),
	(1051,243,'_section_two_body','field_5be866cb9796c'),
	(1052,243,'section_two_courses_0_course_name','Close Protection VIP Team Training'),
	(1053,243,'_section_two_courses_0_course_name','field_5be8672a9796e'),
	(1054,243,'section_two_courses_0_course_description','There is no substitution for the highest level of training and preparedness which SIS provide for all our clients.\r\n\r\nMany of the courses shown below relate to our Close Protection training with bespoke courses designed and delivered in the home country of the students.\r\n\r\nHEAT (Hostile Environment Awareness Training ) is a specially designed three-day course for individuals and groups who may travelling abroad to countries where the security situation may be challenging. Attending this course is essential for you and all your staff before travelling to these areas. Please refer to our Travel Intelligence Division for other important information'),
