	(1067,243,'_section_two_courses_3_course_description','field_5be867359796f'),
	(1068,243,'section_two_courses_4_course_name','Paramedic Training'),
	(1069,243,'_section_two_courses_4_course_name','field_5be8672a9796e'),
	(1070,243,'section_two_courses_4_course_description','These SIS defensive and operational driving courses are an essential part of close protection operations and form part of Close Protection Team training. The courses can be delivered in-country worldwide.\r\n\r\nDrivers, who form part of the close protection team, need to appreciate the high level of threat to their clients, and how to react in the event of any attack or ambush by firearms, explosives or moving vehicles.\r\n\r\nThe SIS courses, delivered by former military Special Forces and Law Enforcement instructors is very much a practical, hands-on course and will equip students how to react in any attack situation.'),
