	(1127,285,'_header','field_5be875cdcb3df'),
	(1128,285,'section_one_title','ELECTRONIC BUGS ON THE MARKET TODAY'),
	(1129,285,'_section_one_title','field_5be8761bcb3e2'),
	(1130,285,'section_one_body','On the open market today, there are literally hundreds of audio and video miniature electronic surveillance devices which are installed in a variety of locations in commercial buildings, private homes, vehicles and many other situations, all of which are a clear threat to your business and private data.'),
	(1131,285,'_section_one_body','field_5be87626cb3e3'),
	(1132,285,'section_one_image','286'),
	(1133,285,'_section_one_image','field_5be87634cb3e4'),
	(1134,285,'section_one',''),
	(1135,285,'_section_one','field_5be875fccb3e1'),
	(1136,285,'section_two_title','OUR CLIENTS'),
	(1137,285,'_section_two_title','field_5be8764dcb3e6'),
	(1138,285,'section_two_body','Our clients include multi-national and ‘blue chip’ companies, government departments, royalty, and hi-net worth individuals. We have carried out TSCM operations throughout the world in all types of buildings, vehicles, aircraft and marine craft including ocean-going vessels. We never disclose our clients or our operations.'),
	(1139,285,'_section_two_body','field_5be87659cb3e7'),
	(1140,285,'section_two',''),
	(1141,285,'_section_two','field_5be87644cb3e5'),
	(1142,285,'section_three_title','ELECTRONIC SURVEILLANCE DEVICES'),
	(1143,285,'_section_three_title','field_5be87682cb3e9'),
	(1144,285,'section_three_body','In our experience at SIS, when the ‘stakes are high’ and businesses and high net worth individuals are targeted, e.g.in hostile take overs, due diligence, investigations of executives, we find that it is a regular occurrence that ‘professional’ audio and video surveillance devices have been planted. These devices are able to penetrate all of your electronic data, telephone and communication systems and can only be detected by highly specialist technicians using state of the art counter surveillance equipment.'),
	(1145,285,'_section_three_body','field_5be87689cb3ea'),
	(1146,285,'section_three',''),
	(1147,285,'_section_three','field_5be87677cb3e8'),
	(1148,285,'section_four_title','COUNTER SURVEILLANCE TEAMS AND CONFIDENTIALITY'),
	(1149,285,'_section_four_title','field_5be876e2cb3ec'),
	(1150,285,'section_four_body','SIS TSCM teams are all highly trained specialists with backgrounds in law enforcement, government and sensitive military units, with a combined total of over 100 years of national and international experience in TSCM and related Cyber Security operations. All our operations are carried out to our clients’ instructions and with the utmost confidentiality. At the conclusion of each TSCM operation we always supply our clients with a confidential and comprehensive report.'),
	(1151,285,'_section_four_body','field_5be876eccb3ed'),
	(1152,285,'section_four',''),
	(1153,285,'_section_four','field_5be876d2cb3eb'),
	(1154,285,'section_five_title','COUNTER SURVEILLANCE EQUIPMENT'),
	(1155,285,'_section_five_title','field_5be87712cb3ef'),
	(1156,285,'section_five_body','With the ever present threat of attack by video and audio devices, the equipment to detect them is constantly changing. SIS regularly updates equipment an operational practises to counter the threat.'),
	(1157,285,'_section_five_body','field_5be87717cb3f0'),
