	(1404,350,'_section_three_subtitle','field_5be9c8ff26da3'),
	(1405,350,'section_three_body','International terrorism, violent crime, insurgency and major civil disturbances are now a fact of life in many countries throughout the world today. You need to have all the information and intelligence available to make those important decisions when travelling abroad. Travel companies do not provide this level of information and you have a duty of care to ensure you have taken all steps to minimise the risks to you and your team.\r\n\r\nSIS provide our clients with up to date information, intelligence, and a risk management service which will ensure that every element of your overseas trips are comprehensively researched giving you all the security information you need before you travel.\r\n\r\nWe work with a number of government agencies and blue-chip countries throughout the world to provide this essential information and support, which can include:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Personal protection in country</li>\r\n 	<li>Personal and asset protection GPS tracking throughout</li>\r\n 	<li>24 Hour monitoring service</li>\r\n 	<li>Interpreters</li>\r\n 	<li>Crisis Support</li>\r\n 	<li>Specialist travel and medical insurance which includes air evacuation and medical treatment</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nWe are partnered with a major international travel company to provide all your travel requirements including international flights on scheduled or private aircraft, hotels, or secure private residences together with specific information regarding visas and inoculations you may require. A detailed itinerary will be provided prior to your travel.'),
