	(2548,494,'section_one_body','The security threat throughout the world is changing almost daily with many Western countries continuing to be on high alert in the wake of international terrorism and cyber-attacks.\r\n\r\nIt is estimated that cyber-attacks worldwide cost companies and governments over 13 billion pounds in 2017 alone. The unprecedented wave of terrorist attacks in the UK, Europe, the USA and the Middle East have caused a complete change in the security strategies of many governments, business organisations and high net worth individual.\r\n\r\nThe international SIS Management Team have security experience in many countries throughout the world including recent conflicts in Iraq, Afghanistan, Syria, Africa South America and many other countries where terrorism and organised crime continues to rise. The unique knowledge and experience of SIS in these areas and the threats posed make us the ideal partner for all your security needs.'),
