	(3307,510,'section_three_body','Our Close Protection Officers who will travel with you if required, are highly experienced former Special Forces and Law Enforcement officers with unique international experience.\r\n\r\nThey are always professional, discreet and can be relied upon in all situations and circumstances.'),
