	(3313,510,'section_four_title','OUR SOLUTION'),
	(3314,510,'_section_four_title','field_5be6ed366770a'),
	(3315,510,'section_four_body','In addition to our close protection services we believe that there is no substitution for the highest level of training and preparedness before travelling and SIS will train our clients, their staff and families during a bespoke Hostile Environment Awareness Training course (HEAT).\r\n\r\nUtilising all the SIS resources we will assist in planning your itinerary, taking account of all visa and local medical requirements, booking hotels, arranging transport, providing interpreters and if necessary liaising with foreign governments and law enforcement officials.\r\n\r\nWe will advise you on all the relevant cultural protocols, personal, corporate finance and insurance requirements for your travel'),
